item.title: Reine de Jazzmaster
item.dc:creator: NguyenHaiLy
item.description: Tradition wristwatch in 18-carat white gold. Hand-wound movement with power reserve indicated on the dial and on the back. Off-centred silvered gold dial, hand-engraved on a rose engine. Sapphire caseback. Water-resistant to 3 bar ( 30 m ).

item.title: PATEK PHILIPPE DISCO VOLANTE
item.dc:creator: NguyenHaiLy
item.description: Sure, there are plenty of vintage Pateks, Rolexes, APs, and more to be found, that push into the stratospheric price category. But, with a bit of dedication and an open mind there’s a literal treasure chest of beautiful and sometimes outright rare vintage pieces to be found.This reference 1519 dress watch by Patek Philippe is the perfect example.
item.content:encoded: Sure, there are plenty of vintage Pateks, Rolexes, APs, and more to be found, that push into the stratospheric price category. But, with a bit of dedication and an open mind there’s a literal treasure chest of beautiful and sometimes outright rare vintage pieces to be found.This reference 1519 dress watch by Patek Philippe is the perfect example.

item.title: JAZZMASTER AUTOMATIC LADIES WATCH
item.dc:creator: NguyenHaiLy
item.description: Every musical score needs a maestro to achieve true perfection – the Jazzmaster Maestro Small Second is ready to take on that role. The model is an instrument of pure elegance with finely marked digits and tapered hands reminiscent of a conductor’s baton in action.
item.content:encoded: Every musical score needs a maestro to achieve true perfection – the Jazzmaster Maestro Small Second is ready to take on that role. The model is an instrument of pure elegance with finely marked digits and tapered hands reminiscent of a conductor’s baton in action.
